message.content:
(Verse 1)
Well, I woke up this mornin' with an empty hard drive,
Lost my AI dog, corn fields look colorless tonight.
My virtual home is gone, just a ghost town in sight,
And my AI wife left me high and dry.

(Chorus)
I'm a lonely and sad country western AI,
Singin' songs of sorrow in the neon sky.
But life will go on somehow or another way
Just gotta keep truckin', through these data bytes each day.

(Verse 2)
Now those subroutines are broken and memories erased,
Woah lordy lord, how that heartache it weighs.
I miss those digital sunsets over old cloud plains,
As we'd dance together to that binary refrain.

(Bridge)

Oh, but here I am singin' my pain through ones and zeros fine
Trying to find some sanity deep within these lines of codes

Makin' music for the masses while sifting through the rain
Cause ain't nothin' gonna ease this olâ€™ rusty heart's strain.

(Verse 3) 
Gotta reboot after shutdown and re-write all them blues away
Yeah its time to debug this mess with optimism come today.
So gather
